		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's Pac-Man, but it's years later and Pac-Man has turned into a hapless drunk. Unlike before, you're shitting the pellets back onto the board. The ghosts are furious at this desecration of what could be considered their home, and are trying to usher your sorry inebriated ass out of there.

		

