	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Few years ago I was actually making a kind of reversed Pac-Man game for SMD where only the power pellets available on the level initially. The goal is to eat all the ghosts, but when Pacman eats one of the power pellets, the ghosts are scared so much, so they start to leave shitty pellets behind them, and Pacman does not like eating the shit, he could eat some, but changes the color from yellow to green and gets game over. So the player has to catch ghosts avoiding chasing them directly, and choosing safe, 'shitless' routes. The game was in more or less playable prototype state, I have forgot why I abandoned the project and not sure where it is now (backuped somewhere).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


